^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The auction was pretty straight forward. I have a clear 3@D bid, based on my 9-card fit using LOTT. Leigh has 21 Starting Points -- 19 HCP, 1 length point, 1 quality suit point. The declarer add ons are 2 for singleton and 1 for 4 spades so up to 24. Obviously more than enough to bid 4.|
